headline: Albemarle (ALB) Surpasses Market Returns: Some Facts Worth Knowing
summary: Albemarle (ALB) reached $194.18 at the closing of the latest trading day, reflecting a +2.33% change compared to its last close.

headline: Comcast Gears Up to Report Q4 Earnings: What's in the Cards?
summary: CMCSA heads into its Q4 earnings with Content & Experiences gaining steam, even as broadband competition and pricing shifts pressure Connectivity results.

headline: Nucor's Q4 Earnings Miss on Lower Volumes, Revenues Beat
summary: NUE posts a Q4 EPS of $1.73, missing estimates as lower steel volumes weigh, even as sales rise 8.6% and management guides for Q1 earnings growth.

headline: CENX and EGA Partner to Build Primary Aluminum Smelter in Oklahoma
summary: CENX and EGA to build a primary aluminum smelter in Oklahoma, the first new U.S. plant since 1980, set to produce 750,000 tons annually.
